sentences: Kang Min-kyung (born August 3, 1990) is a South Korean singer and actress.
She is one half of the duo Davichi, who rose to fame upon the release of their debut album Amaranth in 2008.
Kang has also pursued acting, appearing in television dramas such as Smile, Mom (2010), Vampire Idol (2011), Haeundae Lovers (2012) and family drama The Dearest Lady (2015).
